title: 08/18/2021 DPS Hour 2 Rookie QB Predictions
itunes:title: 08/18/2021 DPS Hour 2 Rookie QB Predictions
description:
LaVar Arrington, TJ Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress, in for Dan, believe it's Cam Newton's job to lose in New England. They debate who will have the best rookie season between Justin Fields, Trevor Lawrence, Mac Jones, Trey Lance and Zach Wilson. Plus, did Jamal Adams get overpaid?
